{"ts": "2026-01-18T21:03:37.325087", "event": "tool_call", "step": 6, "payload": {"tool": "write_file", "arguments": {"file_path": "docs/project_introduction.html", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>CodeMate AI - 新人开发者指南</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 导航栏 -->\n    <nav class=\"navbar\">\n        <div class=\"nav-container\">\n            <div class=\"logo\">\n                <span class=\"logo-icon\">🤖</span>\n                <span class=\"logo-text\">CodeMate AI</span>\n            </div>\n            <ul class=\"nav-menu\">\n                <li><a href=\"#overview\">项目概览</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#capabilities\">核心能力</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#architecture\">架构设计</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#workflow\">工作流程</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#notes\">注意事项</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- 主横幅 -->\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h1 class=\"hero-title\">\n                <span class=\"gradient-text\">CodeMate AI</span>\n            </h1>\n            <p class=\"hero-subtitle\">基于 Function Calling 范式的智能代码分析助手</p>\n            <div class=\"hero-badges\">\n                <span class=\"badge\">v0.3.0</span>\n                <span class=\"badge\">Python 3.10+</span>\n                <span class=\"badge\">GLM-4</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n                <a href=\"#overview\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">开始了解</a>\n                <a href=\"https://github.com\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\">查看源码</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"hero-visual\">\n            <div class=\"code-block\">\n                <div class=\"code-header\">\n                    <span class=\"dot red\"></span>\n                    <span class=\"dot yellow\"></span>\n                    <span class=\"dot green\"></span>\n                </div>\n                <pre class=\"code-content\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> codemate_agent <span class=\"keyword\">import</span> CodeMateAgent\n\nagent = CodeMateAgent()\nresult = agent.run(<span class=\"string\">\"分析这个项目\"</span>)\n<span class=\"comment\"># ✨ 智能分析完成</span></code></pre>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <!-- 项目概览 -->\n    <section id=\"overview\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">项目概览</h2>\n            <p class=\"section-subtitle\">CodeMate AI 是一个帮助开发者快速理解和分析代码的智能助手</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"grid-2\">\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <div class=\"card-icon\">🎯</div>\n                    <h3>项目目标</h3>\n                    <p>帮助开发者快速理解陌生项目的代码结构、搜索和分析代码内容、获取重构建议和最佳实践、自动化代码审查流程。</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <div class=\"card-icon\">💡</div>\n                    <h3>核心理念</h3>\n                    <p>采用原生 Function Calling 范式，通过结构化的工具调用实现更可靠的代码分析，告别文本解析的不确定性。</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"features-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"feature-icon\">✅</span>\n                    <span>原生 Function Calling</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"feature-icon\">✅</span>\n                    <span>模块化工具系统</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"feature-icon\">✅</span>\n                    <span>Pydantic 数据验证</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"feature-icon\">✅</span>\n                    <span>简洁的 CLI 界面</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"feature-icon\">✅</span>\n                    <span>三层日志架构</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <span class=\"feature-icon\">✅</span>\n                    <span>Token 统计</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 核心能力 -->\n    <section id=\"capabilities\" class=\"section section-dark\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">核心能力</h2>\n            <p class=\"section-subtitle\">CodeMate AI 提供全面的代码分析和开发辅助功能</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"capabilities-grid\">\n                <div class=\"capability-card\">\n                    <div class=\"capability-number\">01</div>\n                    <h3>代码分析</h3>\n                    <p>读取和理解代码文件，分析项目结构，识别关键模块和依赖关系</p>\n                    <ul class=\"capability-list\">\n                        <li>文件内容解析</li>\n                        <li>项目结构分析</li>\n                        <li>依赖关系识别</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"capability-card\">\n                    <div class=\"capability-number\">02</div>\n                    <h3>代码搜索</h3>\n                    <p>搜索特定的代码模式，查找函数/类定义，全文搜索代码内容</p>\n                    <ul class=\"capability-list\">\n                        <li>模式匹配搜索</li>\n                        <li>定义查找</li>\n                        <li>全文检索</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"capability-card\">\n                    <div class=\"capability-number\">03</div>\n                    <h3>代码审查</h3>\n                    <p>检查安全漏洞，代码质量评估，最佳实践建议</p>\n                    <ul class=\"capability-list\">\n                        <li>安全漏洞检测</li>\n                        <li>代码质量评估</li>\n                        <li>最佳实践建议</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"capability-card\">\n                    <div class=\"capability-number\">04</div>\n                    <h3>重构建议</h3>\n                    <p>代码优化建议，结构改进方案，性能优化提示</p>\n                    <ul class=\"capability-list\">\n                        <li>代码优化</li>\n                        <li>结构改进</li>\n                        <li>性能提示</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"capability-card\">\n                    <div class=\"capability-number\">05</div>\n                    <h3>任务规划</h3>\n                    <p>自动分解复杂任务，生成执行计划，进度跟踪</p>\n                    <ul class=\"capability-list\">\n                        <li>任务分解</li>\n                        <li>计划生成</li>\n                        <li>进度跟踪</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"capability-card\">\n                    <div class=\"capability-number\">06</div>\n                    <h3>智能对话</h3>\n                    <p>交互式代码问答，持续对话上下文，多轮对话支持</p>\n                    <ul class=\"capability-list\">\n                        <li>代码问答</li>\n                        <li>上下文记忆</li>\n                        <li>多轮对话</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 架构设计 -->\n    <section id=\"architecture\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">架构设计</h2>\n            <p class=\"section-subtitle\">模块化、可扩展的系统架构</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"architecture-diagram\">\n                <div class=\"arch-layer\">\n                    <div class=\"layer-title\">用户层</div>\n                    <div class=\"layer-components\">\n                        <div class=\"component\">CLI 入口</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">交互模式</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">单次查询</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"arch-arrow\">↓</div>\n                \n                <div class=\"arch-layer\">\n                    <div class=\"layer-title\">Agent 核心</div>\n                    <div class=\"layer-components\">\n                        <div class=\"component\">CodeMateAgent</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">循环检测</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">上下文管理</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"arch-arrow\">↓</div>\n                \n                <div class=\"arch-layer\">\n                    <div class=\"layer-title\">工具系统</div>\n                    <div class=\"layer-components\">\n                        <div class=\"component\">文件工具</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">搜索工具</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">Shell 工具</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">Todo 工具</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">Task 工具</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"arch-arrow\">↓</div>\n                \n                <div class=\"arch-layer\">\n                    <div class=\"layer-title\">基础服务</div>\n                    <div class=\"layer-components\">\n                        <div class=\"component\">LLM 客户端</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">日志系统</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">持久化</div>\n                        <div class=\"component\">配置管理</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"modules-grid\">\n                <div class=\"module-card\">\n                    <h4>🤖 Agent 核心</h4>\n                    <p>基于 Function Calling 的智能代理，负责协调工具调用和对话管理</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"module-card\">\n                    <h4>🔧 工具系统</h4>\n                    <p>模块化的工具注册和执行机制，支持文件操作、代码搜索、命令执行等</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"module-card\">\n                    <h4>📊 日志系统</h4>\n                    <p>三层日志架构：运行时日志、Trace 轨迹、Metrics 统计</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"module-card\">\n                    <h4>💾 持久化</h4>\n                    <p>会话存储、记忆管理、会话索引，支持长期记忆和会话回放</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"module-card\">\n                    <h4>🧠 任务规划</h4>\n                    <p>自动检测复杂任务，生成执行计划，跟踪任务进度</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"module-card\">\n                    <h4>⚡ Skill 系统</h4>\n                    <p>预定义的专业任务流程，如代码审查、UI/UX 设计等</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 工作流程 -->\n    <section id=\"workflow\" class=\"section section-dark\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">工作流程</h2>\n            <p class=\"section-subtitle\">从用户输入到最终答案的完整流程</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"workflow-container\">\n                <div class=\"workflow-step\">\n                    <div class=\"step-number\">1</div>\n                    <div class=\"step-content\">\n                        <h4>用户输入</h4>\n                        <p>用户通过 CLI 输入问题或任务</p>\n                        <div class=\"step-code\">\n                            <code>./run.sh \"分析这个项目\"</code>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"workflow-arrow\">→</div>\n\n                <div class=\"workflow-step\">\n                    <div class=\"step-number\">2</div>\n                    <div class=\"step-content\">\n                        <h4>构建请求</h4>\n                        <p>Agent 构建包含工具列表的 LLM 请求</p>\n                        <div class=\"step-code\">\n                            <code>messages + tools → LLM API</code>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"workflow-arrow\">→</div>\n\n                <div class=\"workflow-step\">\n                    <div class=\"step-number\">3</div>\n                    <div class=\"step-content\">\n                        <h4>LLM 推理</h4>\n                        <p>GLM-4 模型分析请求，决定是否调用工具</p>\n                        <div class=\"step-code\">\n                            <code>tool_calls: [list_dir, path: \".\"]</code>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"workflow-arrow\">→</div>\n\n                <div class=\"workflow-step\">\n                    <div class=\"step-number\">4</div>\n                    <div class=\"step-content\">\n                        <h4>工具执行</h4>\n                        <p>执行工具并获取结果</p>\n                        <div class=\"step-code\">\n                            <code>result: [\"codemate_agent/\", \"tests/\", ...]</code>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"workflow-arrow\">→</div>\n\n                <div class=\"workflow-step\">\n                    <div class=\"step-number\">5</div>\n                    <div class=\"step-content\">\n                        <h4>结果返回</h4>\n                        <p>将工具结果返回给 LLM 继续推理</p>\n                        <div class=\"step-code\">\n                            <code>tool message → LLM</code>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"workflow-arrow\">→</div>\n\n                <div class=\"workflow-step\">\n                    <div class=\"step-number\">6</div>\n                    <div class=\"step-content\">\n                        <h4>最终答案</h4>\n                        <p>LLM 生成最终答案并返回给用户</p>\n                        <div class=\"step-code\">\n                            <code>\"这个项目包含以下目录...\"</code>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"workflow-note\">\n                <strong>💡 关键特性：</strong>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Function Calling：</strong>LLM 直接返回结构化的 tool_calls，无需文本解析</li>\n                    <li><strong>自动循环：</strong>Agent 自动处理多轮工具调用，直到获取最终答案</li>\n                    <li><strong>上下文管理：</strong>维护完整的对话历史，支持多轮交互</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 注意事项 -->\n    <section id=\"notes\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">注意事项</h2>\n            <p class=\"section-subtitle\">使用 CodeMate AI 时需要了解的重要信息</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"notes-container\">\n                <div class=\"note-category\">\n                    <h3 class=\"note-category-title\">🔒 安全注意事项</h3>\n                    <div class=\"note-items\">\n                        <div class=\"note-item warning\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">⚠️</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>Shell 命令注入风险</h4>\n                                <p>Shell 工具存在命令注入风险，建议使用命令白名单而非黑名单过滤</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"note-item warning\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">⚠️</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>路径遍历漏洞</h4>\n                                <p>文件操作工具可能访问项目外文件，需要添加路径验证</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"note-item warning\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">⚠️</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>API 密钥安全</h4>\n                                <p>请妥善保管 GLM_API_KEY，不要提交到版本控制系统</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"note-category\">\n                    <h3 class=\"note-category-title\">⚙️ 配置说明</h3>\n                    <div class=\"note-items\">\n                        <div class=\"note-item info\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">ℹ️</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>环境变量配置</h4>\n                                <p>创建 .env 文件并配置 GLM_API_KEY、GLM_MODEL 等参数</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"note-item info\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">ℹ️</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>模型选择</h4>\n                                <p>glm-4-flash 速度快成本低，glm-4-plus 能力更强成本更高</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"note-item info\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">ℹ️</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>日志配置</h4>\n                                <p>支持运行时日志、Trace 轨迹和 Metrics 统计三种日志类型</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"note-category\">\n                    <h3 class=\"note-category-title\">📚 使用建议</h3>\n                    <div class=\"note-items\">\n                        <div class=\"note-item success\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">✅</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>从简单任务开始</h4>\n                                <p>先尝试简单的代码分析任务，熟悉工具的使用方式</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"note-item success\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">✅</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>查看 Trace 日志</h4>\n                                <p>通过 Trace 日志了解 Agent 的决策过程和工具调用情况</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"note-item success\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">✅</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>利用 Skill 系统</h4>\n                                <p>使用预定义的 Skill（如 code-review）快速完成专业任务</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"note-category\">\n                    <h3 class=\"note-category-title\">🐛 已知问题</h3>\n                    <div class=\"note-items\">\n                        <div class=\"note-item error\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">❌</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>API 调用无重试</h4>\n                                <p>网络不稳定时可能导致任务失败，建议手动重试</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"note-item error\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">❌</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>测试覆盖率不足</h4>\n                                <p>核心模块测试覆盖率约 17%，建议谨慎使用</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"note-item error\">\n                            <div class=\"note-icon\">❌</div>\n                            <div class=\"note-content\">\n                                <h4>类型提示不一致</h4>\n                                <p>部分代码使用 list[str]，部分使用 List[str]，需要统一</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"quick-start\">\n                <h3>🚀 快速开始</h3>\n                <div class=\"quick-start-steps\">\n                    <div class=\"qs-step\">\n                        <span class=\"qs-number\">1</span>\n                        <div class=\"qs-content\">\n                            <h4>安装依赖</h4>\n                            <code>pip install -r requirements.txt</code>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"qs-step\">\n                        <span class=\"qs-number\">2</span>\n                        <div class=\"qs-content\">\n                            <h4>配置环境</h4>\n                            <code>cp .env.example .env && 编辑 .env</code>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"qs-step\">\n                        <span class=\"qs-number\">3</span>\n                        <div class=\"qs-content\">\n                            <h4>运行 Agent</h4>\n                            <code>./run.sh</code>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 页脚 -->\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"footer-content\">\n                <div class=\"footer-section\">\n                    <h4>CodeMate AI</h4>\n                    <p>基于 Function Calling 范式的智能代码分析助手</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"footer-section\">\n                    <h4>文档</h4>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"#overview\">项目概览</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#capabilities\">核心能力</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#architecture\">架构设计</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#notes\">注意事项</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"footer-section\">\n                    <h4>资源</h4>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">GitHub</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">API 文档</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">示例项目</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">贡献指南</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"footer-section\">\n                    <h4>版本信息</h4>\n                    <p>当前版本：v0.3.0</p>\n                    <p>Python：3.10+</p>\n                    <p>LLM：GLM-4</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"footer-bottom\">\n                <p>&copy; 2025 CodeMate AI. 基于 MIT License 开源</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"script.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>"}}, "session_id": "s-20260118-205935-055a"}
